{"type": "article", "id": 47950, "title": "让袋泡茶更好用，你可以给它穿个“外套”｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-05T22:52:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 46078, "name": "Digital Habits"}, {"id": 46079, "name": "Tooletries"}, {"id": 46080, "name": "Art Lebedev Studio"}, {"id": 46081, "name": "Loehr"}, {"id": 46082, "name": "Ananthakrishnan"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 165, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171205181638aZ0JChHqx1m3Oi7r.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Aromea Tea Bag by Ananthakrishnan</h3><p>袋泡茶的好处是冲泡便捷，但有研究发现使用后至少有 10％的茶叶提取物被常规的茶叶袋所浪费。</p><p>怎样能更卫生更合理地释放袋泡茶里的“精华”呢？设计团队 Ananthakrishnan 设计了一款名为 Aromea 的创意茶包，其实就是给原有的茶包穿上了一件外套，当你想扔掉茶包时，给它穿上这件“外套”，然后使劲挤压，就可以把茶包中最浓缩精华的汁液留下来。它也允许你在喝茶时控制茶的浓度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205181923FpHnAUhTQOwu5BzS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703409\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051819241prRqZDsHvUF4POK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703409\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051819240uUEMB3yVmRZ5N4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703409\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205181925IipPFHDvLl1Bq2mJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205181926gvrjkIBGlLoE697q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703409\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Germany-made collection by Loehr</h3><p>创立于 2012 年的德国家具品牌 Loehr 最近为其 Germany-made 系列再添新品，包括搁架、长凳、双人沙发和小餐桌，极简主义和荷兰风格派运动成为这次新品的灵感来源，主张纯抽象和纯朴，外形上缩减到几何形状。</p><p>除了推新品，Loehr 还为现有产品推出了一系列新的颜色和材料，或是采用粉末涂层，或是镜面抛光处理，更大胆地加入了绿色、天蓝色和黄色等饱和度较高的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182041LnTrEP8MbteX7wVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182042Fn8l45fB1UIeyNzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182042BqFr5suT2OUY63P8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182043e4w3qZWiSsNQCKYO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182043CwM2QZjeaiTxmGsL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.536802\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182051F84TUq7HOzWuxgDh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670051\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Loehr</figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Nugget by David Baron &amp; Ryan Cocca</h3><p>谈到 The Nugget，设计师喜欢说“你不要把它只用来坐”。的确，这个四件套包括一个坚实的折叠底座，一个柔软的折叠座垫，和两个支撑靠枕，可以布置成沙发、床、躺椅、简易帐篷或其他各种各样的其他配置，比如儿童们想要建立一个堡垒。你可以把它当成家具，或者用于和孩子们玩游戏，可能性很多。售价 229 美元，<a href=\"https://www.nuggetcomfort.com/solid-nuggets\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182138iLvSfekE5p2PduQm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.731250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051821395qVdxMXU0ahEeHSD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584896\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182140SIcknws9eJQouUHC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504257\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182141gTC0uRxAePYn5vWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504257\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182145yokDNTlYc5nmr8Av.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504257\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Nugget</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Urnus-14 by Art Lebedev Studio</h3><p>俄罗斯设计工作室 Art Lebedev Studio 擅长给城市公共环境设计一些小的配件设施，比如这款名为 Urnus-14 的户外垃圾桶，小巧而易于使用。与其他整体式垃圾桶相比，它几乎精简了所有多余结构，仅有一个框架，可以用内置的橡皮筋将垃圾袋固定，确保它不会滑出支架的凹槽，一个色彩鲜明的垃圾袋就可以让其脱颖而出，在公共环境中辨识度也极高。它的好处在于不需要额外清洁，取出垃圾袋换上新的即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182209bDUxSe0g1tWnjTkp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656190\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182209BlFd5sT93tuR6XAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182210gZYvXnBJUDF5bkSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755238\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Art Lebedev Studio</figcaption></figure></div><h3>The No-Screw, No-Glue Toothbrush Holder by Josh &amp; Saul Cockburn of Tooletries</h3><p>你可能不想在浴室的墙面使用电钻之类的暴力手段，Tooletries 这款硅橡胶牙刷架可以是你的替代解决方案。它无需钻孔，也不需要借助任何物品，只需要找一块平坦的表面，比如瓷砖、大理石，甚至是玻璃，将其内部的空气排空，便可以牢固贴附于表面，可以收纳牙刷、牙膏、剃须刀或是首饰小物，最高承重可达 9 公斤，不使用时也很容易剥离。售价 15308 日元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/Tooletries-Mighty-Toothbrush-Holder-Charcoal/dp/B019H34XKI/ref=sr_1_1?tag=yankodesign-22&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510792063&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=tooletries&amp;th=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0514f7jmi8&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182244cwHCmbnKO47jRQrG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182245jv9i6tDU0ag4hVb8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182245prd4yUkF16MVKYaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182246aoTzIs7bHyBC0Q4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Tooletries</figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Ambient Light Color Swing by Digital Habits</h3><p>连接设备制造商 Digital Habits 最新推出一款吊灯，名为 Color Swing。它的功能就像其名字所描述的那样，可以根据颜色变换不同的光色。吊灯内置了一个传感器，可以检测到附近物体的颜色，然后改变自己的光线来匹配这个物体。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a05144wy96b&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182448fEX1RqCliIerjV7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565909\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017120518244939Pm0Hi8tREFqSnd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565909\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205182451fTC0ZpnOhtAKNBWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565909\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Digital Habits</figcaption></figure></div>"}